        "reaction_type_english": "Cracking reaction",
        "description": "在实验室规模的滴流床反应器中，使用Ni-Zeolite β催化剂和氢气，在350-450°C和30 bar压力下，对生物油的主要成分油酸进行加氢裂化，将其转化为喷气燃料范围的烃类（壬烷、癸烷、十二烷）。",
        "text_snippet": "The hydrocracking of oleic acid was performed in a laboratory scale trickle-bed reactor in the presence of a Ni–Zeolite 𝜷 catalyst and hydrogen for hydrogenation... The hydrocracking reactions were performed at different reaction bed temperatures with the operating conditions as shown in Table 2.",
